{"tid":1872521,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"喂！香城眾籌緊本地口罩生產，有錢出錢冇錢推post啦！","createTime":"2020-02-10T06:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T07:35:02.000Z","uid":254729,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cb70a52a6c1c64260a3059895ae6ad54ed98db95","tid":1872521,"uid":254729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:30:46.000Z","msg":"原ｐｏｓｔ：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1870702/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1870702/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌連結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://goget.fund/39oEP2R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoget.fund%2F39oEP2R&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=cc840ef1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goget.fund/39oEP2R</a><br />\n<br />\n捐＄２００以上可以於正式發售前可優先購買1盒口罩<br />\n今次係實質有用野，<br />\n但反而反應比較低，希望大家幫幫手有錢出錢有力推post"},{"pid":"f4bc8233c0fe6a0b860d4c41e25703dd820c0784","tid":1872521,"uid":254729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:35:20.000Z","msg":"１／２０"},{"pid":"9024524aa740830dc22e84fdb1d1a70736bc25d1","tid":1872521,"uid":175556,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:39:05.000Z","msg":"有無微微實際成果比人睇下先，唔想單靠信仰捐錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9457f75fa7c047ac268fec20768a194032b1be93","tid":1872521,"uid":134012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:40:57.000Z","msg":"無菌室整唔整到都成問題"},{"pid":"9381a331ceeb5eb0d82f9e4e39c32a374f9c1d3a","tid":1872521,"uid":306340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:43:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6854287c807e3c08097d79a09734cf0c248af707","tid":1872521,"uid":202872,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:44:11.000Z","msg":"我比較想知捐完錢俾你生產口罩<br />\n大家買到足夠口罩直到肺炎消失<br />\n禁d機留番俾你繼續生產繼續賣？<br />\n<br />\n即係所有人打本俾你做生意？<br />\n會唔會有其他方法確保唔會有人血饅頭<br />\n例如請手足做工人 利潤捐一部分支援手足<br />\n如果冇詳細計劃好難捐得落手<br />\n定係其實有做呢d野我唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42804cc370bdeafcdc22927616af85b30d598b3b","tid":1872521,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:44:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b80ebcee1a1c06a5b6f51a8d5defafe54568019e","tid":1872521,"uid":211364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:45:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b4aca98488b8fe4439288b1e3039ff2ea78c4d46","tid":1872521,"uid":121307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:45:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"02ecc7a74c6e08a4294aaf380d35f47ae0908862","tid":1872521,"uid":225117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ba4cb736f36955fd1a849f3e742ba627f05d57","tid":1872521,"uid":194912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6854287c807e3c08097d79a09734cf0c248af707","tid":1872521,"uid":202872,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:44:11.000Z","msg":"我比較想知捐完錢俾你生產口罩<br />\n大家買到足夠口罩直到肺炎消失<br />\n禁d機留番俾你繼續生產繼續賣？<br />\n<br />\n即係所有人打本俾你做生意？<br />\n會唔會有其他方法確保唔會有人血饅頭<br />\n例如請手足做工人 利潤捐一部分支援手足<br />\n如果冇詳細計劃好難捐得落手<br />\n定係其實有做呢d野我唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:48:52.000Z","msg":"佢有呢種諗法同埋渠道去做<br />\n如果做到俾佢賺都係OK 都係供需<br />\n其實最怕係捐完冇作為<br />\n呢點真係難保證"},{"pid":"7c44b217d0b2cded0d132aec2f6b0b375ba095ee","tid":1872521,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eaa609e78e8f02fca5552aa63f0ab051e56a622","tid":1872521,"uid":322821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:49:32.000Z","msg":"ASTM level 1唔夠咯。<br />\n&quot;Level 1: low barrier protection for general use for low-risk, nonsurgical procedures and exams that do not involve aerosols, sprays and fluids. An ear loop mask is a level 1 mask. ASTM level 1 masks are the general standard for both surgical and procedural use.&quot;<br />\n如果要防最好要ASTM level 2以上<br />\n&quot;Level 2: moderate barrier protection for low-to-moderate levels of aerosols, sprays and fluids.<br />\n<br />\nLevel 3: maximum barrier protection for any situation that has the potential for exposure to heavy levels of aerosols, sprays and fluids. Cardinal Health recommends this level as a best practice for supporting OR safety initiatives.&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.beckershospitalreview.com/quality/the-4-fs-of-medical-mask-selection.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.beckershospitalreview.com%2Fquality%2Fthe-4-fs-of-medical-mask-selection.html&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=baf8c5d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.beckershospitalreview.com/quality/the-4-fs-of-medical-mask-selection.html</a><br />\n醫院非常時期應該要有ASTM level 3<br />\n平時人出街應該都至少level 2啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c5dfdcb6c93f522db8c79a9c8a60c7ab70b974","tid":1872521,"uid":126054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daae9d829a92830e778a135ec7e163e9f9b47dab","tid":1872521,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:50:30.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=5dc5c414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"73cfc0fe948aac01135a2dbd0393bfc315c5edee","tid":1872521,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c8ba4cb736f36955fd1a849f3e742ba627f05d57","tid":1872521,"uid":194912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6854287c807e3c08097d79a09734cf0c248af707","tid":1872521,"uid":202872,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:44:11.000Z","msg":"我比較想知捐完錢俾你生產口罩<br />\n大家買到足夠口罩直到肺炎消失<br />\n禁d機留番俾你繼續生產繼續賣？<br />\n<br />\n即係所有人打本俾你做生意？<br />\n會唔會有其他方法確保唔會有人血饅頭<br />\n例如請手足做工人 利潤捐一部分支援手足<br />\n如果冇詳細計劃好難捐得落手<br />\n定係其實有做呢d野我唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:48:52.000Z","msg":"佢有呢種諗法同埋渠道去做<br />\n如果做到俾佢賺都係OK 都係供需<br />\n其實最怕係捐完冇作為<br />\n呢點真係難保證"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:50:48.000Z","msg":"哩啲不嬲都係講往績<br />\nGet tv 之前化驗做咗好多野啦"},{"pid":"3809e2e0ab446e159bc191f86955afd27b1d8fe8","tid":1872521,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:57:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada212ffb615c0ebdb2646036a0f5e4b2198a42a","tid":1872521,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d535124a96f1fba354e69c469ac5050b2272e2a8","tid":1872521,"uid":311579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":